><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ibc1665703195980.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ibc1665703195980.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ibc1665703195980.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ibc1665703195980\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get dynamic information about the Uniface Router.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__section_kbq_5wk_gwb\">\n<p class=\"lines\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__lines_fnv_5wk_gwb\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">operation GET_UROUTER_DYN</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">params</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\"> entity UROUTERD.UROUTMON : OUT</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">endparams</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__section_jjl_wwk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1086146e66\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">UROUTERD.UROUTMON—single occurrence of entity UROUTERD.UROUTMON containing dynamic\n        information about the Uniface Router.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">UROUTERD.UROUTMON entity</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__1\">Fieldname</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__2\">Packing Code</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__3\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">pid</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__4\">Uniface Router's process ID</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">privileged</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__2\">B2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__3\">Boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__4\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code> if this monitor has a privileged\n                                connection, <code class=\"ph codeph\">F</code> if not </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">state</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__2\">C2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__4\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">I</code>=idle, <code class=\"ph codeph\">B</code>=busy, <code class=\"ph codeph\">E</code>=exiting\n                </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">maxclients</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__2\">I2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__4\">Maximum clients allowed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">maxservers</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__2\">I2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__4\">Maximum servers allowed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">maxmons</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__2\">I2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__4\">Maximum monitors allowed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">response</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__4\">Ticks taken for this monitor to get this entity from the Uniface Router\n                </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ioprint</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__4\">Value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ioprint</span> of Uniface Router</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">msgtoclients</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__2\">C256</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ibc1665703195980__table_cn2_zwk_gwb__entry__4\">Message returned on unsuccessful connect</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__section_sd5_fxk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1086146e294\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If successful, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to zero. Otherwise, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html#qln1665702528769__section_fbt_4d2_gwb\">Return Codes</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__section_url_hxk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1086146e310\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ibc1665703195980__section_h1g_3xk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1086146e319\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">GET_UROUTER_DYN</span> operation gets dynamic information about the Uniface\n        Router.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528456\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528456\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "GET_UROUTER_DYN Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get dynamic information about the Uniface Router. operation GET_UROUTER_DYN params entity UROUTERD.UROUTMON : OUT endparams Parameters UROUTERD.UROUTMON—single occurrence of entity UROUTERD.UROUTMON containing dynamic information about the Uniface Router. Table 1. UROUTERD.UROUTMON entity Fieldname Packing Code Data Type Description pid I4 Numeric Uniface Router's process ID privileged B2 Boolean T if this monitor has a privileged connection, F if not state C2 String I =idle, B =busy, E =exiting maxclients I2 Numeric Maximum clients allowed maxservers I2 Numeric Maximum servers allowed maxmons I2 Numeric Maximum monitors allowed response I4 Numeric Ticks taken for this monitor to get this entity from the Uniface Router ioprint I4 Numeric Value of $ioprint of Uniface Router msgtoclients C256 String Message returned on unsuccessful connect Return Values If successful, $status is set to zero. Otherwise, see Return Codes . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The GET_UROUTER_DYN operation gets dynamic information about the Uniface Router. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}